  <T n="entry_text">0x1FB9EFDE<!--String: "Hothead Rock Geyser"--></T>
  <V n="entry_text_description" t="enabled">
    <T n="enabled">0xE3E508B5<!--String: "Hothead Rock Geyser is one of the oldest known formations at Gibbi Point. It may even predate the Great Wave itself, though there are conflicting opinions on that one. Not only have Sims learned its volcanic secret, but Plumbirds have taken advantage of the lava blast as well as there's another winged treat they like to enjoy that appears only when the geyser erupts with lava."--></T>
